snippet.title: Rynn's Adventure Extended Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Rynn's Adventure: Trouble in the Enchanted Forest.

Rynn's Adventure is Arcane Four Studio's multi-platform video game targeted for release on Steam(Windows, Mac), Wii U, and Xbox One.

Learn more at http://www.rynnsadventure.com
